White blocks at 1 to make an eye on the left side.  But now Black can double dansu at 2 and White is going to lose some stones.

White might try 3 to capture Black thinking that's his ticket to living, but when Black plays 4 White only has one liberty.  White cannot capture 4 so \cf1\b White is dead.\cf0\b0
