Therefore what do we think about White's tiger's mouth at 1.

Black can still play 2 which hits at exactly the right spot.  White will dansu at 5 but then Black takes a liberty away at 6.  White cannot make an eye because he doesn't have enough liberties to do so.  \cf1\b White is still dead.\cf0\b0

This means the final answer is:

